Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.14,0:01:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Igaiga, we'll be arriving{\i0}\N{\i1}in Kagoshima soon.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.97,0:01:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}-I'm getting nervous.{\i0}\N{\i1}-Yeah.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.56,0:01:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.73,0:01:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was just remembering.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.15,0:01:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The first time I took this ferry{\i0}\N{\i1}to Hinoshima, your hometown.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.07,0:01:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Were you nervous?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.82,0:02:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nervous? More like anxious, I’d say.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.24,0:02:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What a place.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.12,0:02:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing but mountains and sea.\NI've sure traveled far.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.17,0:02:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When we first met, you were so startled{\i0}\N{\i1}that you fell down!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.30,0:02:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When I first saw you,{\i0}\N{\i1}I thought you were a boy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.23,0:02:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That’s so mean!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.64,0:02:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was really looking forward{\i0}\N{\i1}to your arrival!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.82,0:02:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just like yourself, the people on this{\i0}\N{\i1}island are full of personality.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.28,0:02:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At first, your grandpa seemed scary.{\i0}\N{\i1}I didn't like him very much.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.29,0:02:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But Grandpa Gon{\i0}\N{\i1}was always looking out for you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.83,0:02:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My tea is murky.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.96,0:02:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}His eyes are a dull grey.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.42,0:02:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichiga Igarashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.97,0:03:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Iga-Iga!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.85,0:03:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.43,0:03:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.39,0:03:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, it’s Kazuyoshi Igarashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.60,0:03:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so you’re Igaiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.15,0:03:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Aunt Setsu was kind from the start, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.69,0:03:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She was. Come to think of it,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.40,0:03:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Aunt Setsu was the first person{\i0}\N{\i1}to call me Igaiga.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.95,0:03:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And the breakfast she made me was so good!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.41,0:03:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Here you are.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.75,0:03:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I've brought the museum director.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.04,0:03:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.12,0:03:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The director is technically my superior,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.17,0:03:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but I was so relieved{\i0}\N{\i1}by how approachable he was.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.30,0:03:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,-What’s his name again?\N-It's Kento Hidaka, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.55,0:03:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,-Oh, right.\N-Do you remember Bunpei's full name?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.39,0:03:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Bunpei... Bunpei... Tarou!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.56,0:03:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Osamu Fumihira! Don't forget!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.94,0:03:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What did you think{\i0}\N{\i1}when you first met Yoko?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.32,0:04:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Her? Oh, well, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.70,0:04:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,-Hi Yoko.\N-Keep driving, Bunpei!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.92,0:04:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,-Takuma, too.\N-I'll stop the bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.63,0:04:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s play soccer!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.38,0:04:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The police officer,{\i0}\N{\i1}the teacher, Wataru, and Yuma.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.51,0:04:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You got along with everyone right away.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.89,0:04:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}-Even though you have a scary face!{\i0}\N{\i1}-You were the fastest to fit in!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.85,0:04:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't forget the island's wildlife!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.14,0:04:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Those beautiful sunset-red feathers.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.35,0:04:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And goats were just walking around!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.98,0:04:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And that insect!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.74,0:04:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You got stung on the butt!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.53,0:04:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was so unbelievably itchy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.91,0:04:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The creatures on the island are amazing!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.58,0:04:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Red fur, Tokara horses, goats,\Ngiant eels, Bunpei, and that insect!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.00,0:04:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. Did you include Bunpei in that list?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.59,0:04:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Bunpei?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.42,0:05:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But the most surprising thing{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.13,0:05:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}was the island's incredible golf course!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.93,0:05:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.14,0:05:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.24,0:05:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.28,0:05:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,They used the natural coastal terrain\Nto create a full-on links course!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.08,0:05:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The islanders built it\Nfor their own enjoyment!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.17,0:05:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a headwind today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.84,0:05:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm taking the shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.30,0:05:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She grips the club like a baseball bat.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.22,0:05:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This really is just for fun.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.69,0:06:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She has an extreme open stance,{\i0}\N{\i1}facing directly towards the sea.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.15,0:06:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For a shot like this,{\i0}\N{\i1}you need to hit a low, strong draw.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.70,0:06:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But she uses a thin three iron for it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.66,0:06:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For a girl, it's quite a long, stiff club.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.41,0:06:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I guess she's expecting a big slice.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.51,0:06:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.47,0:06:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Like a swallow before the rain,\Nslipping under the wind!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.14,0:06:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What was that follow-through?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.47,0:06:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,There it goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.56,0:06:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.65,0:06:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'd never seen a kid play like you did.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.11,0:06:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I thought you must be a monster!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.16,0:06:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A monster? That's so mean!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.20,0:06:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, it's a compliment!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.95,0:07:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}-It means you left a big impression!{\i0}\N{\i1}-Don't call me a monster!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.54,0:07:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What was your first impression{\i0}\N{\i1}of me, Tonbo?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.71,0:07:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well, you’ve got a scary face.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.76,0:07:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,A really scary face.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.43,0:07:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Your face is really scary, Igaiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.73,0:07:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Okay, next topic.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.11,0:07:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At first, I didn't understand{\i0}\N{\i1}anything about you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.57,0:07:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You refused to leave the island.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.12,0:07:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m staying.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.70,0:07:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm staying on this island forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.75,0:07:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m not going anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.88,0:07:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.76,0:07:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the pride of the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.77,0:08:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It feels like time has stopped here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.07,0:08:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder which ones are my mom and dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.25,0:08:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,They say people\Nturn into stars when they die.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.17,0:08:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I understood the reason you learned{\i0}\N{\i1}to play golf with a three iron.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.46,0:08:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I remember you cried then.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.38,0:08:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was just the starlight{\i0}\N{\i1}stinging my eyes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.93,0:08:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}-Is that so?{\i0}\N{\i1}-Of course!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.22,0:08:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sorry, I got carried away.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.77,0:08:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What will you do about high school?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.86,0:08:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,There’s only a middle school\Non the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.41,0:08:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m not going to high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.99,0:09:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m staying on the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.66,0:09:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I tried all kinds of ways{\i0}\N{\i1}to show you a new world.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.08,0:09:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yeah!{\i0}\N{\i1}You gave me a wedge!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.46,0:09:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was my first club{\i0}\N{\i1}besides the three iron!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.72,0:09:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The grip contained your father’s memories.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.10,0:09:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet you'd like to try it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.56,0:09:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.35,0:09:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you have the wedge,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.36,0:09:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll teach you something\Nthat you can’t do with a three iron.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.72,0:10:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna try too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.76,0:10:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.06,0:10:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn’t it beautiful?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.81,0:10:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like the sun is melting into the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.40,0:10:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Putting a bench here was a great idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.70,0:10:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Playing golf with you and watching the{\i0}\N{\i1}sunset from that bench was wonderful.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.45,0:10:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.70,0:10:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It reminded me how fun golf can be,{\i0}\N{\i1}as obvious as it may be.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.75,0:10:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But you said something{\i0}\N{\i1}really harsh after that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.05,0:10:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonbo, what you’re doing isn’t golf.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.26,0:10:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not golf?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.51,0:10:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wanted to challenge{\i0}\N{\i1}you and your play style.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.43,0:10:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Challenge?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.02,0:10:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right! And boy did you ever!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.77,0:10:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsubura!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.07,0:10:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,-Yoko’s niece.\N-Tsubura Adaniya!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.42,0:11:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tsubura was completely different{\i0}\N{\i1}from anyone I had played golf with before.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.17,0:11:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She was so good that for the first time,{\i0}\N{\i1}I felt all jittery about playing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.09,0:11:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes. She really gave you{\i0}\N{\i1}the challenge you needed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.43,0:11:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A three-quarter shot with a driver?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.35,0:11:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.23,0:11:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.32,0:11:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsubura only swings from here to here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.19,0:11:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And you still send it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.20,0:11:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I always use a three-quarter swing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.32,0:11:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how I'll become Japan's best.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.99,0:11:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Japan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.03,0:11:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.08,0:11:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The coach told me\Nthat if I master the three-quarter shot,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.50,0:11:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I can be the best in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.04,0:11:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,After that, I can learn a full shot\Nwhen I aim to conquer the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.80,0:12:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.63,0:12:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,She's Tonbo's age\Nand already taking on the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.26,0:12:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I don't want to lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.69,0:12:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tsubura seemed half impressed{\i0}\N{\i1}and half astonished by your golf.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.82,0:12:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe the one-legged stance was too much.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.40,0:12:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.20,0:12:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.99,0:12:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,She opened the club face!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.79,0:12:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do next, Tonbo?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.21,0:12:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tsubura seemed truly{\i0}\N{\i1}shocked by the way you played.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.71,0:12:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She was holding her head.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.30,0:12:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was just doing things like I always do.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.68,0:12:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tsubura will be your rival someday.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.35,0:12:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I’m convinced of that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.18,0:12:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder what Tsubura thought?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.27,0:12:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Same as me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.73,0:12:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She wanted you to keep playing golf.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.61,0:13:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s why she said\Nsome harsh things to you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.19,0:13:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.11,0:13:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s keep going!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.03,0:13:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What’s your dream, Tonbo?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.57,0:13:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.91,0:13:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want to become?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.95,0:13:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you aiming for?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.75,0:13:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to stay on the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.96,0:13:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.17,0:13:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.67,0:13:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.17,0:13:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just going to stay here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.09,0:13:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that your dream, Tonbo?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.51,0:13:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That sounds kind of boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.93,0:13:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Your life will be empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.97,0:13:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,This island has everything I need.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.14,0:13:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Flying fish and red-bearded deer!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.85,0:13:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s not boring at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.19,0:13:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m fine here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.69,0:13:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m going to live here\Nfor the rest of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.36,0:13:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you’re not just\Nconvincing yourself of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.07,0:13:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you’re just avoiding the fact\Nthat there’s a whole world out there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.62,0:13:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,There may be even more beautiful sights.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.62,0:14:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was shocked at first when she said that,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.34,0:14:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but after that,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.25,0:14:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I learned about Tsubura's{\i0}\N{\i1}true passion for golf.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.63,0:14:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He's been driving\Nthe same old truck for years.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.89,0:14:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,My father, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.97,0:14:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all rusted.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.89,0:14:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And the bed is full of holes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.56,0:14:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Letting your kid\Nplay golf can be expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.40,0:14:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to get really good at golf.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.61,0:14:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to buy my dad a new truck.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.57,0:14:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And there's something\NI want you to have, Tonbo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.70,0:14:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was so surprised{\i0}\N{\i1}when she gave me that club.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.66,0:14:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was convinced.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.46,0:14:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}-That Tsubura would be your rival--{\i0}\N{\i1}-You already said that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.50,0:14:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care of it and use it all up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.09,0:14:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This was the idea of the person{\i0}\N{\i1}who designed the course.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.84,0:14:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He figured it would{\i0}\N{\i1}create a six-hole course.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.51,0:14:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Didn’t everyone on the island{\i0}\N{\i1}design that course together?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.56,0:14:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,They built it, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.23,0:15:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But the design was done by Mr. Kuta alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.52,0:15:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s go see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.40,0:15:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The person who designed the course.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.32,0:15:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s go together, Tonbo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.28,0:15:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.78,0:15:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At first, I was really scared.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.87,0:15:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I promised to never leave the island,{\i0}\N{\i1}but you took me to Akureki Island.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.12,0:15:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Scarier than my face?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.33,0:15:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're hesitating?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.04,0:15:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But you know,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.25,0:15:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was surprised when{\i0}\N{\i1}you talked about yourself.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.68,0:15:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.72,0:15:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I knew I had to tell you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.72,0:15:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to be a professional golfer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.98,0:15:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Used to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.73,0:15:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I lost golf, my family,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.53,0:15:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and most of all my pride as a pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.03,0:15:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But still, humans need to eat, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.74,0:16:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s kind of funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.79,0:16:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to learn\Nmore about golf, Tonbo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.01,0:16:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was surprised by your tears.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.85,0:16:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I’m sure it took a lot of courage{\i0}\N{\i1}for you to talk about that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.73,0:16:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's when I realized I had to be{\i0}\N{\i1}courageous, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.98,0:16:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tonbo, you're...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.61,0:16:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We went to meet{\i0}\N{\i1}Mr. Kuta on Akureki Island.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.62,0:16:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He lived in such an incredible place.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.99,0:16:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The path to his front door{\i0}\N{\i1}was like an animal's trail!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.21,0:16:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this really Mr. Kuta's house?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.58,0:16:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.30,0:16:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,St. Andrews at sunset.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.05,0:16:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Or maybe it was sunrise.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.43,0:16:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I've seen it countless times on TV, but\Nthis leaves a different impression.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.72,0:17:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.23,0:17:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard you built\Na small course on this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.19,0:17:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.03,0:17:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,-Yes, I think so.\N-Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.65,0:17:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you let Tonbo play there?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.79,0:17:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What a beautiful course!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.45,0:17:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s totally different from Hinoshima!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.75,0:17:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You had told me, Igaiga.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.88,0:17:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You said the course was...\NWhat was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.63,0:17:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,"Supper difficult!"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.46,0:17:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Super difficult!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.17,0:17:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,"Supper" doesn't make any sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.98,0:17:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Go! Flying fish ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.57,0:17:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Flying fish, turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.95,0:18:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Climb, climb!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.88,0:18:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.92,0:18:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kuta's single-hole course\Nwas so much fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.22,0:18:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And supper difficult.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.18,0:18:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Super!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.30,0:18:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You’re saying that on purpose!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.64,0:18:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.23,0:18:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you think of the island?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.57,0:18:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Playing a new hole,\Nand the fastest green you've ever seen!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.57,0:18:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.16,0:18:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It was fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.70,0:18:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It was so fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.45,0:18:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Taking you to Akureki Island{\i0}\N{\i1}was the right decision.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.12,0:18:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I truly believe so.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.67,0:18:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You know,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.13,0:18:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I think I finally understand all the{\i0}\N{\i1}things you’ve been telling me, Igaiga.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.09,0:18:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh? And what did I tell you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.93,0:19:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Um...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.22,0:19:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Okay, let's move on then!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.47,0:19:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.02,0:19:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I’ve got four clubs.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.19,0:19:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Igaiga, Tsubura.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.90,0:19:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kuta, too!\NAnd of course...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.74,0:19:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom and Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.91,0:19:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I've made a big decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.75,0:19:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ve made my choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.13,0:19:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Next spring, I’m leaving the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.18,0:19:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's your diploma, Tonbo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.89,0:19:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You grew so much from{\i0}\N{\i1}the end of summer to graduation.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.85,0:19:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Next thing I knew you were in uniform.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.35,0:19:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What’s wrong, Igaiga?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.57,0:19:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was such a joy to watch you grow up.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.78,0:20:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They say you get more{\i0}\N{\i1}emotional as you get older.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.57,0:20:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You may have gotten bigger, but I don't{\i0}\N{\i1}like a kid like you telling me that!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.83,0:20:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Stop making that scary face while crying!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.42,0:20:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t oversleep tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.76,0:20:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.01,0:20:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,On this last night,\NI didn't know what to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.02,0:20:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though there were\Nso many things I wanted to talk about.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.19,0:20:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was Grandpa Gon who always{\i0}\N{\i1}pushed me forward and supported me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.69,0:20:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That’s right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.19,0:20:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No one in the world cares{\i0}\N{\i1}about you more than Grandpa Gon.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.91,0:20:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You've all made me who I am today!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.45,0:20:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.58,0:20:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m off!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.22,0:21:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I won’t forget you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.89,0:21:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm your grandpa\Nand you're my granddaughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.56,0:21:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,-Grandpa Gon.\N-Anytime!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.32,0:21:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You can come back anytime!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.78,0:21:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If things get tough,\Ncome back to your old gramps!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.49,0:21:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You can always return to this island!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.33,0:21:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandpa Gon. Grandpa Gon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.04,0:21:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m off!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.50,0:21:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m off!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.42,0:21:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandpa Gon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.88,0:21:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a good look, Tonbo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.43,0:21:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That island is your hometown.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.76,0:21:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s where your story began.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.89,0:21:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a home you should be proud of.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.94,0:21:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a good look.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.86,0:22:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonbo, this is just the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.23,0:22:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.69,0:22:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s finally happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.11,0:22:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! You can see Kagoshima!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.61,0:22:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, the lights are incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.28,0:22:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,-How about we get some good food?\N-Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.75,0:22:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You can treat me to\Nan all-you-can-eat meal!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.37,0:22:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Wait just a minute, Tonbo.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.18,0:23:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.56,0:23:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So those are the eyes of someone\Nraised only looking at the horizon?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.56,0:24:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Here comes Tonbo.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.81,0:24:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,On the next Oi! Tonbo!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.94,0:24:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonbo's Course Debut!
